186937,64,145,2,7,1,35,5,Gocaroti atthi gocaro atthi agocaro. 
186938,64,146,2,6,1,21,3,Tattha katamo agocaro? 
186939,64,146,7,59,1,447,44,"Idhekacco vesiyāgocaro vā hoti vidhavā, thullakumārikā, paṇḍaka, bhikkhunī, pānāgāragocaro vā hoti, saṃsaṭṭho viharati rājūhi rājamahāmattehi titthiyehi titthiyasāvakehi ananulomikena saṃsaggena, yāni vā pana tāni kulāni assaddhāni appasannāni anopānabhūtāni akkosakaparibhāsakāni anatthakāmāni ahitakāmāni aphāsukakāmāni ayogakkhemakāmāni bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ upāsakānaṃ upāsikānaṃ, tathārūpāni kulāni sevati bhajati payirupāsati, ayaṃ vuccati agocaro. "
186940,64,147,2,5,1,20,3,Tattha katamo gocaro? 
186941,64,147,6,59,1,349,41,"Idhekacco na vesiyāgocaro vā hoti… pe… na pānāgāragocaro vā hoti, asaṃsaṭṭho viharati rājūhi… pe… titthiyasāvakehi ananulomikena saṃsaggena, yāni vā pana tāni kulāni saddhāni pasannāni opānabhūtāni kāsāvapajjotāni isivātapaṭivātāni atthakāmāni… pe… yogakkhemakāmāni bhikkhūnaṃ… pe… upāsikānaṃ, tathārūpāni kulāni sevati bhajati payirupāsati, ayaṃ vuccati gocaro. "
186942,64,147,60,90,1,143,19,"Iti iminā ca ācārena iminā ca gocarena upeto hoti samupeto upagato samupagato upapanno sampanno samannāgato, tena vuccati‘‘ ācāragocarasampanno’’ ti( vibha.511). "
186943,64,148,2,8,1,47,6,Api cettha imināpi nayena ācāragocarā veditabbā. 
186944,64,148,9,15,1,37,6,Duvidho hi anācāro kāyiko vācasiko ca. 
186945,64,148,16,20,1,28,4,Tattha katamo kāyiko anācāro? 
186946,64,148,21,160,1,1021,110,"Idhekacco saṅghagatopi acittīkārakato there bhikkhū ghaṭṭayantopi tiṭṭhati, ghaṭṭayantopi nisīdati, puratopi tiṭṭhati, puratopi nisīdati, uccepi āsane nisīdati, sasīsampi pārupitvā nisīdati, ṭhitakopi bhaṇati, bāhāvikkhepakopi bhaṇati, therānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ anupāhanānaṃ caṅkamantānaṃ saupāhano caṅkamati, nīce caṅkame caṅkamantānaṃ ucce caṅkame caṅkamati, chamāya caṅkamantānaṃ caṅkame caṅkamati, there bhikkhū anupakhajjāpi tiṭṭhati, anupakhajjāpi nisīdati, navepi bhikkhū āsanena paṭibāhati, jantāgharepi there bhikkhū anāpucchā kaṭṭhaṃ pakkhipati, dvāraṃ pidahati, udakatitthepi there bhikkhū ghaṭṭayantopi otarati, puratopi otarati, ghaṭṭayantopi nhāyati, puratopi nhāyati, ghaṭṭayantopi uttarati, puratopi uttarati, antaragharaṃ pavisantopi there bhikkhū ghaṭṭayantopi gacchati, puratopi gacchati, vokkamma ca therānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ purato purato gacchati, yānipi tāni honti kulānaṃ ovarakāni gūḷhāni ca paṭicchannāni ca yattha kulitthiyo kulakumāriyo nisīdanti, tatthapi sahasā pavisati, kumārakassapi sīsaṃ parāmasati, ayaṃ vuccati kāyiko anācāro. "
186947,64,149,2,6,1,30,4,Tattha katamo vācasiko anācāro? 
186948,64,149,7,15,1,77,8,Idhekacco saṅghagatopi acittīkārakato there bhikkhū anāpucchā dhammaṃ bhaṇati. 
186949,64,149,16,35,1,134,15,"Pañhaṃ vissajjeti, pātimokkhaṃ uddisati, ṭhitakopi bhaṇati, bāhāvikkhepakopi bhaṇati, antaragharaṃ paviṭṭhopi itthiṃ vā kumāriṃ vā evamāha–"
186950,64,149,36,60,1,119,16,"‘‘ itthannāme itthaṃgotte kiṃ atthi, yāgu atthi, bhattaṃ atthi, khādanīyaṃ atthi, kiṃ pivissāma, kiṃ khādissāma, kiṃ bhuñjissāma. "
186951,64,149,61,79,1,63,10,"Kiṃ vā me dassathā’’ ti vippalapati, ayaṃ vuccati vācasiko anācāro( mahāni.87). "
186952,64,149,80,84,1,40,4,Paṭipakkhavasena panassa ācāro veditabbo. 
186953,64,150,2,37,1,383,33,"Apica bhikkhu sagāravo sappatisso hirottappasampanno sunivattho supāruto pāsādikena abhikkantena paṭikkantena ālokitena vilokitena samiñjitena pasāritena okkhittacakkhu iriyāpathasampanno indriyesu guttadvāro bhojane mattaññū jāgariyamanuyutto satisampajaññena samannāgato appiccho santuṭṭho āraddhavīriyo ābhisamācārikesu sakkaccakārī garucittīkārabahulo viharati, ayaṃ vuccati ācāro. "
186954,64,150,38,42,1,25,4,Evaṃ tāva ācāro veditabbo. 
186955,64,151,2,8,1,70,6,Gocaro pana tividho upanissayagocaro ārakkhagocaro upanibandhagocaroti. 
186956,64,151,9,12,1,30,3,Tattha katamo upanissayagocaro? 
186957,64,151,13,33,1,142,15,"Dasakathāvatthuguṇasamannāgato kalyāṇamitto, yaṃ nissāya assutaṃ suṇāti, sutaṃ pariyodapeti, kaṅkhaṃ vitarati, diṭṭhiṃ ujuṃ karoti, cittaṃ pasādeti. "
186958,64,151,34,53,1,113,14,"Yassa vā pana anusikkhamāno saddhāya vaḍḍhati, sīlena, sutena, cāgena, paññāya vaḍḍhati, ayaṃ vuccati upanissayagocaro. "
186959,64,152,2,4,1,20,2,Katamo ārakkhagocaro? 
186960,64,152,5,52,1,280,37,"Idha bhikkhu antaragharaṃ paviṭṭho vīthiṃ paṭipanno okkhittacakkhu yugamattadassāvī susaṃvuto gacchati, na hatthiṃ olokento, na assaṃ, na rathaṃ, na pattiṃ, na itthiṃ, na purisaṃ olokento, na uddhaṃ ullokento, na adho olokento, na disāvidisaṃ pekkhamāno gacchati, ayaṃ vuccati ārakkhagocaro. "
186961,64,153,2,4,1,24,2,Katamo upanibandhagocaro? 
186962,64,153,5,10,1,48,5,Cattāro satipaṭṭhānā yattha cittaṃ upanibandhati. 
186963,64,153,11,14,1,21,2,Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā –
186964,64,153,15,27,1,52,8,"‘‘ ko ca, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno gocaro sako pettiko visayo? "
186965,64,153,28,47,1,62,7,"Yadidaṃ cattāro satipaṭṭhānā’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.372), ayaṃ vuccati upanibandhagocaro. "
186966,64,153,48,60,1,59,10,Iti iminā ca ācārena iminā ca gocarena upeto… pe… samannāgato. 
186967,64,153,61,64,1,36,3,Tenapi vuccati ācāragocarasampannoti. 
186968,64,154,2,11,1,121,8,Aṇumattesu vajjesu {bhayadassāvī}ti aṇuppamāṇesu asañcicca āpannasekhiyaakusalacittuppādādibhedesu vajjesu bhayadassanasīlo. 
186969,64,154,12,25,1,99,11,"Samādāya sikkhati {sikkhāpadesū}ti yaṃkiñci sikkhāpadesu sikkhitabbaṃ, taṃ sabbaṃ sammā ādāya sikkhati. "
186970,64,154,26,41,1,108,10,Ettha ca‘‘ pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto’’ ti ettāvatā ca puggalādhiṭṭhānāya desanāya pātimokkhasaṃvarasīlaṃ dassitaṃ.
186971,64,154,42,60,1,121,13,"‘‘ Ācāragocarasampanno’’ tiādi pana sabbaṃ yathāpaṭipannassa taṃ sīlaṃ sampajjati, taṃ paṭipattiṃ dassetuṃ vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
186972,64,155,2,2,1,19,1,Indriyasaṃvarasīlaṃ 
186973,64,156,2,27,1,141,16,"15. Yaṃ panetaṃ tadanantaraṃ‘‘ so cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā’’ tiādinā nayena dassitaṃ indriyasaṃvarasīlaṃ, tattha {so}ti pātimokkhasaṃvarasīle ṭhito bhikkhu. "
186974,64,156,28,39,1,109,10,Cakkhunā rūpaṃ {disvā}ti kāraṇavasena cakkhūti laddhavohārena rūpadassanasamatthena cakkhuviññāṇena rūpaṃ disvā. 
186975,64,156,40,62,1,146,16,"Porāṇā panāhu‘‘ cakkhu rūpaṃ na passati, acittakattā, cittaṃ na passati, acakkhukattā, dvārārammaṇasaṅghaṭṭe pana cakkhupasādavatthukena cittena passati. "
186976,64,156,63,84,1,126,16,"Īdisī panesā‘ dhanunā vijjhatī’ tiādīsu viya sasambhārakathā nāma hoti, tasmā cakkhuviññāṇena rūpaṃ disvāti ayamevettha attho’’ ti. "
186977,64,156,85,99,1,125,12,"Na {nimittaggāhī}ti itthipurisanimittaṃ vā subhanimittādikaṃ vā kilesavatthubhūtaṃ nimittaṃ na gaṇhāti, diṭṭhamatteyeva saṇṭhāti. "
186978,64,156,100,122,1,229,18,"{Nānubyañjanaggāhī}ti kilesānaṃ anuanubyañjanato pākaṭabhāvakaraṇato anubyañjananti laddhavohāraṃ hatthapādasitahasitakathitavilokitādibhedaṃ ākāraṃ na gaṇhāti, yaṃ tattha bhūtaṃ, tadeva gaṇhāti, cetiyapabbatavāsī mahātissatthero viya. "
186979,64,157,2,27,1,257,24,Theraṃ kira cetiyapabbatā anurādhapuraṃ piṇḍacāratthāya āgacchantaṃ aññatarā kulasuṇhā sāmikena saddhiṃ bhaṇḍitvā sumaṇḍitapasādhitā devakaññā viya kālasseva anurādhapurato nikkhamitvā ñātigharaṃ gacchantī antarāmagge disvā vipallatthacittā mahāhasitaṃ hasi. 
186980,64,157,28,37,1,85,9,Thero kimetanti olokento tassā dantaṭṭhike asubhasaññaṃ paṭilabhitvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
186981,64,157,38,40,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
186982,64,158,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Tassā dantaṭṭhikaṃ disvā, pubbasaññaṃ anussari; "
186983,64,159,2,12,1,44,7,"Tattheva so ṭhito thero, arahattaṃ apāpuṇī’’ ti. "
186984,64,160,2,22,1,92,13,"Sāmikopi kho panassā anumaggaṃ gacchanto theraṃ disvā‘‘ kiñci, bhante, itthiṃ passathā’’ ti pucchi. "
186985,64,160,23,26,1,13,3,Taṃ thero āha–
186986,64,161,2,12,1,39,8,"‘ ‘ Nābhijānāmi itthī vā, puriso vā ito gato; "
186987,64,162,2,10,1,43,5,"Apica aṭṭhisaṅghāṭo, gacchatesa mahāpathe’’ ti. "
186988,64,163,2,21,1,213,19,Yatvādhikaraṇamenan tiādimhi yaṃkāraṇā yassa cakkhundriyāsaṃvarassa hetu etaṃ puggalaṃ satikavāṭena cakkhundriyaṃ asaṃvutaṃ apihitacakkhudvāraṃ hutvā viharantaṃ ete abhijjhādayo dhammā anvāssaveyyuṃ anubandheyyuṃ. 
186989,64,163,22,31,1,91,8,Tassa saṃvarāya {paṭipajjatī}ti tassa cakkhundriyassa satikavāṭena pidahanatthāya paṭipajjati. 
186990,64,163,32,42,1,90,9,"Evaṃ paṭipajjantoyeva ca rakkhati cakkhundriyaṃ, cakkhundriye saṃvaraṃ āpajjatītipi vuccati. "
186991,64,163,43,51,1,57,8,Tattha kiñcāpi cakkhundriye saṃvaro vā asaṃvaro vā natthi. 
186992,64,163,52,61,1,61,9,Na hi cakkhupasādaṃ nissāya sati vā muṭṭhasaccaṃ vā uppajjati. 
186993,64,163,62,79,1,162,16,"Apica yadā rūpārammaṇaṃ cakkhussa āpāthaṃ āgacchati, tadā bhavaṅge dvikkhattuṃ uppajjitvā niruddhe kiriyamanodhātu āvajjanakiccaṃ sādhayamānā uppajjitvā nirujjhati. "
186994,64,163,80,83,1,33,3,Tato cakkhuviññāṇaṃ dassanakiccaṃ. 
186995,64,163,84,87,1,40,3,Tato vipākamanodhātu sampaṭicchanakiccaṃ. 
186996,64,163,88,91,1,49,3,Tato vipākāhetukamanoviññāṇadhātu santīraṇakiccaṃ. 
186997,64,163,92,102,1,113,9,"Tato kiriyāhetukamanoviññāṇadhātu voṭṭhabbanakiccaṃ sādhayamānā uppajjitvā nirujjhati, tadanantaraṃ javanaṃ javati. "
186998,64,164,2,14,1,88,11,"Tatrāpi neva bhavaṅgasamaye, na āvajjanādīnaṃ aññatarasamaye saṃvaro vā asaṃvaro vā atthi. "
186999,64,164,15,32,1,110,16,"Javanakkhaṇe pana sace dussīlyaṃ vā muṭṭhasaccaṃ vā aññāṇaṃ vā akkhanti vā kosajjaṃ vā uppajjati, asaṃvaro hoti. "
187000,64,164,33,40,1,50,7,Evaṃ honto pana so cakkhundriye asaṃvaroti vuccati. 
187001,64,164,41,42,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
187002,64,164,43,54,1,79,9,"Yasmā tasmiṃ sati dvārampi aguttaṃ hoti, bhavaṅgampi āvajjanādīnipi vīthicittāni . "
187003,64,164,55,57,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
187004,64,164,58,75,1,157,16,"Yathā nagare catūsu dvāresu asaṃvutesu kiñcāpi antogharadvārakoṭṭhakagabbhādayo susaṃvutā honti, tathāpi antonagare sabbaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ arakkhitaṃ agopitameva hoti. "
187005,64,164,76,99,1,177,20,"Nagaradvārena hi pavisitvā corā yadicchanti, taṃ kareyyuṃ, evameva javane dussīlyādīsu uppannesu tasmiṃ asaṃvare sati dvārampi aguttaṃ hoti, bhavaṅgampi āvajjanādīnipi vīthicittāni. "
187006,64,165,2,14,1,91,10,"Tasmiṃ pana sīlādīsu uppannesu dvārampi guttaṃ hoti, bhavaṅgampi āvajjanādīnipi vīthicittāni. "
187007,64,165,15,17,1,9,2,Yathā kiṃ? 
187008,64,165,18,33,1,130,14,"Yathā nagaradvāresu saṃvutesu kiñcāpi antogharādayo asaṃvutā honti, tathāpi antonagare sabbaṃ bhaṇḍaṃ surakkhitaṃ sugopitameva hoti. "
187009,64,165,34,52,1,142,16,"Nagaradvāresu hi pihitesu corānaṃ paveso natthi, evameva javane sīlādīsu uppannesu dvārampi guttaṃ hoti, bhavaṅgampi āvajjanādīnipi vīthicittāni. "
187010,64,165,53,59,1,61,6,Tasmā javanakkhaṇe uppajjamānopi cakkhundriye saṃvaroti vutto. 
187011,64,166,2,7,1,39,5,Sotena saddaṃ sutvātiādīsupi eseva nayo. 
187012,64,166,8,14,1,110,6,Evamidaṃ saṅkhepato rūpādīsu kilesānubandhanimittādiggāhaparivajjanalakkhaṇaṃ indriyasaṃvarasīlanti veditabbaṃ. 
187013,64,167,2,2,1,20,1,Ājīvapārisuddhisīlaṃ 
187014,64,168,2,28,1,222,20,"16. Idāni indriyasaṃvarasīlānantaraṃ vutte ājīvapārisuddhisīle ājīvahetu paññattānaṃ channaṃ sikkhāpadānanti yāni tāni‘‘ ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā pāpiccho icchāpakato asantaṃ abhūtaṃ uttarimanussadhammaṃ ullapati, āpatti pārājikassa. "
187015,64,168,29,36,1,68,6,"Ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā sañcarittaṃ samāpajjati, āpatti saṅghādisesassa. "
187016,64,168,37,54,1,108,14,"Ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā‘ yo te vihāre vasati so bhikkhu arahā’ ti bhaṇati, paṭivijānantassa āpatti thullaccayassa. "
187017,64,168,55,67,1,108,11,"Ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā bhikkhu paṇītabhojanāni agilāno attano atthāya viññāpetvā bhuñjati, āpatti pācittiyassa. "
187018,64,168,68,80,1,113,11,"Ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā bhikkhunī paṇītabhojanāni agilānā attano atthāya viññāpetvā bhuñjati, āpatti pāṭidesanīyassa. "
187019,64,168,81,112,1,166,21,"Ājīvahetu ājīvakāraṇā sūpaṃ vā odanaṃ vā agilāno attano atthāya viññāpetvā bhuñjati , āpatti dukkaṭassā’’ ti( pari.287) evaṃ paññattāni cha sikkhāpadāni, imesaṃ channaṃ sikkhāpadānaṃ. "
187020,64,169,2,11,1,44,6,"Kuhanātiādīsu ayaṃ pāḷi,‘‘ tattha katamā kuhanā? "
187021,64,169,12,34,1,226,21,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassa pāpicchassa icchāpakatassa yā paccayapaṭisevanasaṅkhātena vā sāmantajappitena vā iriyāpathassa vā aṭṭhapanā ṭhapanā saṇṭhapanā bhākuṭikā bhākuṭiyaṃ kuhanā kuhāyanā kuhitattaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati kuhanā."
187022,64,170,2,8,1,20,4,‘ ‘ Tattha katamā lapanā? 
187023,64,170,9,31,1,231,21,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassa pāpicchassa icchāpakatassa yā paresaṃ ālapanā lapanā sallapanā ullapanā samullapanā unnahanā samunnahanā ukkācanā samukkācanā anuppiyabhāṇitā cāṭukamyatā muggasūpyatā pāribhaṭyatā, ayaṃ vuccati lapanā."
187024,64,171,2,7,1,25,4,‘ ‘ Tattha katamā nemittikatā? 
187025,64,171,8,23,1,161,14,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassa pāpicchassa icchāpakatassa yaṃ paresaṃ nimittaṃ nimittakammaṃ obhāso obhāsakammaṃ sāmantajappā parikathā, ayaṃ vuccati nemittikatā."
187026,64,172,2,7,1,25,4,‘ ‘ Tattha katamā nippesikatā? 
187027,64,172,8,28,1,213,19,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassa pāpicchassa icchāpakatassa yā paresaṃ akkosanā vambhanā garahanā ukkhepanā samukkhepanā khipanā saṃkhipanā pāpanā sampāpanā avaṇṇahārikā parapiṭṭhimaṃsikatā, ayaṃ vuccati nippesikatā."
187028,64,173,2,9,1,41,6,‘ ‘ Tattha katamā lābhena lābhaṃ nijigīsanatā? 
187029,64,173,10,25,1,120,14,"Lābhasakkārasilokasannissito pāpiccho icchāpakato ito laddhaṃ āmisaṃ amutra harati, amutra vā laddhaṃ āmisaṃ idha āharati. "
187030,64,173,26,50,1,123,16,"Yā evarūpā āmisena āmisassa eṭṭhi gaveṭṭhi pariyeṭṭhi esanā gavesanā pariyesanā, ayaṃ vuccati lābhena lābhaṃ nijigīsanatā’’ ti( vibha.862-865). "
187031,64,174,2,10,1,38,5,17. Imissā pana pāḷiyā evamattho veditabbo. 
187032,64,174,11,23,1,123,9,"Kuhananiddese tāva {lābhasakkārasilokasannissitassā}ti lābhañca sakkārañca kittisaddañca sannissitassa, patthayantassāti attho. "
187033,64,174,24,27,1,37,2,{Pāpicchassā}ti asantaguṇadīpanakāmassa. 
187034,64,174,28,35,1,55,5,"{Icchāpakatassā}ti icchāya apakatassa, upaddutassāti attho. "
187035,64,175,2,10,1,114,8,Ito paraṃ yasmā paccayapaṭisevanasāmantajappanairiyāpathasannissitavasena mahāniddese tividhaṃ kuhanavatthu āgataṃ. 
187036,64,175,11,18,1,78,7,Tasmā tividhampetaṃ dassetuṃ paccayapaṭisevanasaṅkhātena vāti evamādi āraddhaṃ. 
