187406,64,263,11,27,1,153,15,"Paṭilābhakālepi hi dhātuvasena vā paṭikūlavasena vā paccavekkhitvā ṭhapitāni cīvarādīni tato uttari paribhuñjantassa anavajjova paribhogo, paribhogakālepi. "
187407,64,263,28,31,1,35,3,Tatrāyaṃ sanniṭṭhānakaro vinicchayo– 
