187409,64,264,13,21,1,89,8,Tatra saṅghamajjhepi nisīditvā paribhuñjantassa dussīlassa paribhogo theyyaparibhogo nāma. 
187410,64,264,22,27,1,52,5,Sīlavato apaccavekkhitvā paribhogo iṇaparibhogo nāma. 
187411,64,264,28,41,1,150,11,"Tasmā cīvaraṃ paribhoge paribhoge paccavekkhitabbaṃ, piṇḍapāto ālope ālope, tathā asakkontena purebhattapacchābhattapurimayāmamajjhimayāmapacchimayāmesu. "
