187958,64,538,43,57,1,127,13,"Aparikkhittagāme yaṃ sabbapaccantimassa gharassa dvāre ṭhito mātugāmo bhājanena udakaṃ chaḍḍeti, tassa patanaṭṭhānaṃ gharūpacāro. "
187959,64,538,58,66,1,53,7,"Tato vuttanayena eko leḍḍupāto gāmo, dutiyo gāmūpacāro. "
187960,64,539,2,22,1,92,11,Araññaṃ pana vinayapariyāye tāva‘‘ ṭhapetvā gāmañca gāmūpacārañca sabbametaṃ araññan’’ ti( pārā.92) vuttaṃ. 
187961,64,539,23,42,1,74,8,"Abhidhammapariyāye‘‘ nikkhamitvā bahi indakhīlā, sabbametaṃ araññan’’ ti( vibha.529) vuttaṃ. "
