187995,64,556,2,20,1,110,10,"32. Rukkhamūlikaṅgampi‘‘ channaṃ paṭikkhipāmi, rukkhamūlikaṅgaṃ samādiyāmī’’ ti imesaṃ aññataravacanena samādinnaṃ hoti. "
187996,64,557,2,27,1,221,19,"Tena pana rukkhamūlikena sīmantarikarukkhaṃ, cetiyarukkhaṃ, niyyāsarukkhaṃ, phalarukkhaṃ, vaggulirukkhaṃ, susirarukkhaṃ, vihāramajjhe ṭhitarukkhanti ime rukkhe vivajjetvā vihārapaccante ṭhitarukkho gahetabboti idamassa vidhānaṃ. "
