188303,64,680,2,23,1,164,16,"41. Kathaṃ {bhāvetabbo}ti ettha pana yo tāva ayaṃ lokiyalokuttaravasena duvidhotiādīsu ariyamaggasampayutto samādhi vutto, tassa bhāvanānayo paññābhāvanānayeneva saṅgahito. "
