188523,64,722,67,99,1,173,24,"‘‘ Dhovāhāvuso, na mayā ābhataṃ, aññehi ābhatan’’ ti vuttena pana yattha ācariyo na passati, evarūpe paṭicchanne vā okāse, abbhokāse vihārassāpi vā ekamante nisīditvā pādā dhovitabbā. "
188524,64,723,2,11,1,77,9,Sace ācariyo telanāḷiṃ āharati uṭṭhahitvā ubhohi hatthehi sakkaccaṃ gahetabbā. 
188525,64,723,12,32,1,101,15,"Sace hi na gaṇheyya,‘‘ ayaṃ bhikkhu ito eva paṭṭhāya sambhogaṃ kopetī’’ ti ācariyassa aññathattaṃ bhaveyya. "
188526,64,723,33,39,1,40,6,Gahetvā pana na āditova pādā makkhetabbā. 
188527,64,723,40,50,1,68,9,"Sace hi taṃ ācariyassa gattabbhañjanatelaṃ bhaveyya, na sāruppaṃ siyā. "
188528,64,723,51,57,1,47,5,Tasmā sīsaṃ makkhetvā khandhādīni makkhetabbāni.
188529,64,723,58,90,1,159,21,"‘‘ Sabbapārihāriyatelamidaṃ, āvuso, pādepi makkhehī’’ ti vuttena pana thokaṃ sīse katvā pāde makkhetvā‘‘ imaṃ telanāḷiṃ ṭhapemi, bhante’’ ti vatvā ācariye gaṇhante dātabbā. "
188530,64,724,2,13,1,75,9,"Āgatadivasato paṭṭhāya kammaṭṭhānaṃ me, bhante, kathetha iccevaṃ na vattabbaṃ. "
188531,64,724,14,26,1,94,11,"Dutiyadivasato pana paṭṭhāya sace ācariyassa pakatiupaṭṭhāko atthi, taṃ yācitvā vattaṃ kātabbaṃ. "
188532,64,724,27,35,1,47,7,"Sace yācitopi na deti, okāse laddheyeva kātabbaṃ. "
188533,64,724,36,41,1,69,5,Karontena khuddakamajjhimamahantāni tīṇi dantakaṭṭhāni upanāmetabbāni. 
