188745,64,782,15,26,1,85,10,"Tesu hi ānāpānanimittaṃ tāva vaḍḍhayato vātarāsiyeva vaḍḍhati, okāsena ca paricchinnaṃ. "
188746,64,782,27,34,1,57,7,Iti sādīnavattā okāsena ca paricchinnattā na vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. 
188747,64,782,35,54,1,126,16,"Brahmavihārā sattārammaṇā, tesaṃ nimittaṃ vaḍḍhayato sattarāsiyeva vaḍḍheyya, na ca tena attho atthi, tasmā tampi na vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. "
188748,64,782,55,82,1,94,13,"Yaṃ pana vuttaṃ‘‘ mettāsahagatena cetasā ekaṃ disaṃ pharitvā’’ ti( dī. ni.1.556) ādi, taṃ pariggahavaseneva vuttaṃ. "
