188868,64,809,86,89,1,31,3,Evarūpe mahāvihārepi vihātabbaṃ. 
188869,64,810,2,9,1,52,6,"Navavihāre bahu navakammaṃ hoti, akarontaṃ ujjhāyanti. "
188870,64,810,10,30,1,121,15,"Yattha pana bhikkhū evaṃ vadanti‘‘ āyasmā yathāsukhaṃ samaṇadhammaṃ karotu, mayaṃ navakammaṃ karissāmā’’ ti evarūpe vihātabbaṃ. "
188871,64,811,2,17,1,142,13,"Jiṇṇavihāre pana bahu paṭijaggitabbaṃ hoti, antamaso attano senāsanamattampi appaṭijaggantaṃ ujjhāyanti, paṭijaggantassa kammaṭṭhānaṃ parihāyati. "
188872,64,812,2,7,1,63,5,Panthanissite mahāpathavihāre rattindivaṃ āgantukā sannipatanti. 
188873,64,812,8,19,1,84,11,Vikāle āgatānaṃ attano senāsanaṃ datvā rukkhamūle vā pāsāṇapiṭṭhe vā vasitabbaṃ hoti. 
188874,64,812,20,26,1,51,6,Punadivasepi evamevāti kammaṭṭhānassa okāso na hoti. 
188875,64,812,27,36,1,62,8,"Yattha pana evarūpo āgantukasambādho na hoti, tattha vihātabbaṃ. "
188876,64,813,2,33,1,269,27,"Soṇḍī nāma pāsāṇapokkharaṇī hoti, tattha pānīyatthaṃ mahājano samosarati, nagaravāsīnaṃ rājakulūpakattherānaṃ antevāsikā rajanakammatthāya āgacchanti, tesaṃ bhājanadārudoṇikādīni pucchantānaṃ asuke ca asuke ca ṭhāneti dassetabbāni honti, evaṃ sabbakālampi niccabyāvaṭo hoti. "
188877,64,814,2,20,1,192,17,"Yattha nānāvidhaṃ sākapaṇṇaṃ hoti, tatthassa kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā divāvihāraṃ nisinnassāpi santike sākahārikā gāyamānā paṇṇaṃ uccinantiyo visabhāgasaddasaṅghaṭṭanena kammaṭṭhānantarāyaṃ karonti. "
188878,64,815,2,13,1,77,9,"Yattha pana nānāvidhā mālāgacchā supupphitā honti, tatrāpi tādisoyeva upaddavo. "
188879,64,816,2,37,1,228,26,"Yattha nānāvidhaṃ ambajambupanasādiphalaṃ hoti, tattha phalatthikā āgantvā yācanti, adentassa kujjhanti, balakkārena vā gaṇhanti, sāyanhasamaye vihāramajjhe caṅkamantena te disvā‘‘ kiṃ upāsakā evaṃ karothā’’ ti vuttā yathāruci akkosanti. "
188880,64,816,38,40,1,25,2,Avāsāyapissa parakkamanti. 
188881,64,817,2,32,1,255,27,"Patthanīye pana leṇasammate dakkhiṇagirihatthikucchicetiyagiricittalapabbatasadise vihāre viharantaṃ ayamarahāti sambhāvetvā vanditukāmā manussā samantā osaranti, tenassa na phāsu hoti, yassa pana taṃ sappāyaṃ hoti, tena divā aññatra gantvā rattiṃ vasitabbaṃ. "
188882,64,818,2,21,1,185,16,"Nagarasannissite visabhāgārammaṇāni āpāthamāgacchanti, kumbhadāsiyopi ghaṭehi nighaṃsantiyo gacchanti, okkamitvā maggaṃ na denti, issaramanussāpi vihāramajjhe sāṇiṃ parikkhipitvā nisīdanti. "
188883,64,819,2,30,1,215,25,"Dārusannissaye pana yattha kaṭṭhāni ca dabbupakaraṇarukkhā ca santi, tattha kaṭṭhahārikā pubbe vuttasākapupphahārikā viya aphāsuṃ karonti, vihāre rukkhā santi, te chinditvā gharāni karissāmāti manussā āgantvā chindanti. "
188884,64,819,31,55,1,158,18,"Sace sāyanhasamayaṃ padhānagharā nikkhamitvā vihāramajjhe caṅkamanto te disvā‘‘ kiṃ upāsakā evaṃ karothā’’ ti vadati, yathāruci akkosanti, avāsāyapissa parakkamanti. "
188885,64,820,2,25,1,167,20,"Yo pana khettasannissito hoti samantā khettehi parivārito, tattha manussā vihāramajjheyeva khalaṃ katvā dhaññaṃ maddanti, pamukhesu sayanti, aññampi bahuṃ aphāsuṃ karonti. "
188886,64,820,26,52,1,167,19,"Yatrāpi mahāsaṅghabhogo hoti, ārāmikā kulānaṃ gāvo rundhanti, udakavāraṃ paṭisedhenti, manussā vīhisīsaṃ gahetvā‘‘ passatha tumhākaṃ ārāmikānaṃ kamman’’ ti saṅghassa dassenti. "
188887,64,820,53,64,1,104,10,"Tena tena kāraṇena rājarājamahāmattānaṃ gharadvāraṃ gantabbaṃ hoti, ayampi khettasannissiteneva saṅgahito. "
188888,64,821,2,30,1,210,23,"Visabhāgānaṃ puggalānaṃ {atthitā}ti yattha aññamaññaṃ visabhāgaverī bhikkhū viharanti, ye kalahaṃ karontā mā, bhante, evaṃ karothāti vāriyamānā etassa paṃsukūlikassa āgatakālato paṭṭhāya naṭṭhāmhāti vattāro bhavanti. "
188889,64,822,2,29,1,171,23,"Yopi udakapaṭṭanaṃ vā thalapaṭṭanaṃ vā nissito hoti, tattha abhiṇhaṃ nāvāhi ca satthehi ca āgatamanussā okāsaṃ detha, pānīyaṃ detha, loṇaṃ dethāti ghaṭṭayantā aphāsuṃ karonti. "
188890,64,823,2,8,1,58,6,Paccantasannissite pana manussā buddhādīsu appasannā honti. 
188891,64,824,2,5,1,35,3,Rajjasīmasannissite rājabhayaṃ hoti. 
188892,64,824,6,21,1,89,14,"Tañhi padesaṃ eko rājā na mayhaṃ vase vattatīti paharati, itaropi na mayhaṃ vase vattatīti. "
188893,64,824,22,32,1,66,9,"Tatrāyaṃ bhikkhu kadāci imassa rañño vijite vicarati, kadāci etassa. "
