188904,64,826,2,19,1,127,16,Kalyāṇamittānaṃ {alābho}ti yattha na sakkā hoti ācariyaṃ vā ācariyasamaṃ vā upajjhāyaṃ vā upajjhāyasamaṃ vā kalyāṇamittaṃ laddhuṃ. 
