188913,64,833,2,2,1,13,1,Anurūpavihāro 
188914,64,834,2,16,1,88,9,"53. Yo pana gocaragāmato nātidūranāccāsannatādīhi pañcahaṅgehi samannāgato, ayaṃ anurūpo nāma. "
188915,64,834,17,19,1,21,2,Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā–
188916,64,834,20,29,1,54,5,"‘‘ kathañca, bhikkhave, senāsanaṃ pañcaṅgasamannāgataṃ hoti? "
188917,64,834,30,56,1,282,21,"Idha, bhikkhave, senāsanaṃ nātidūraṃ hoti nāccāsannaṃ gamanāgamanasampannaṃ, divā appākiṇṇaṃ rattiṃ appasaddaṃ appanigghosaṃ, appaḍaṃsamakasavātātapasarīsapasamphassaṃ, tasmiṃ kho pana senāsane viharantassa appakasireneva uppajjanti cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārā. "
188918,64,834,57,103,1,334,38,"Tasmiṃ kho pana senāsane therā bhikkhū viharanti bahussutā āgatāgamā dhammadharā vinayadharā mātikādharā, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripucchati paripañhati‘ idaṃ, bhante, kathaṃ imassa ko attho’ ti, tassa te āyasmanto avivaṭañceva vivaranti, anuttānīkatañca uttānīkaronti, anekavihitesu ca kaṅkhaṭṭhāniyesu dhammesu kaṅkhaṃ paṭivinodenti. "
188919,64,834,104,124,1,57,7,"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, senāsanaṃ pañcaṅgasamannāgataṃ hotī’’ ti( a. ni.10.11). "
188920,64,835,2,17,1,92,11,Ayaṃ ‘‘ samādhibhāvanāya ananurūpaṃ vihāraṃ pahāya anurūpe vihāre viharantenā’’ ti ettha vitthāro. 
188921,64,836,2,2,1,17,1,Khuddakapalibodhā 
188922,64,837,2,19,1,123,12,"54. Khuddakapalibodhupacchedaṃ {katvā}ti evaṃ patirūpe vihāre viharantena yepissa te honti khuddakapalibodhā, tepi upacchinditabbā. "
188923,64,837,20,25,1,49,4,"Seyyathidaṃ, dīghāni kesanakhalomāni chinditabbāni. "
188924,64,837,26,32,1,52,6,Jiṇṇacīvaresu daḷhīkammaṃ vā tunnakammaṃ vā kātabbaṃ. 
188925,64,837,33,36,1,25,3,Kiliṭṭhāni vā rajitabbāni. 
188926,64,837,37,44,1,37,6,"Sace patte malaṃ hoti, patto pacitabbo. "
188927,64,837,45,47,1,29,2,Mañcapīṭhādīni sodhetabbānīti.
188928,64,837,48,58,1,55,6,‘‘ Ayaṃ khuddakapalibodhupacchedaṃ katvā’’ ti ettha vitthāro. 
188929,64,838,2,2,1,15,1,Bhāvanāvidhānaṃ 
188930,64,839,2,20,1,135,13,55. Idāni sabbaṃ bhāvanāvidhānaṃ aparihāpentena {bhāvetabbo}ti ettha ayaṃ pathavīkasiṇaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbakammaṭṭhānavasena vitthārakathā hoti. 
188931,64,840,2,21,1,195,18,Evaṃ upacchinnakhuddakapalibodhena hi bhikkhunā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantena bhattasammadaṃ paṭivinodetvā pavivitte okāse sukhanisinnena katāya vā akatāya vā pathaviyā nimittaṃ gaṇhitabbaṃ. 
188932,64,840,22,23,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
188933,64,841,2,37,1,187,26,"‘ ‘ Pathavīkasiṇaṃ uggaṇhanto pathaviyaṃ nimittaṃ gaṇhāti kate vā akate vā sāntake, no anantake, sakoṭiye, no akoṭiye, savaṭṭume, no avaṭṭume, sapariyante, no apariyante, suppamatte vā sarāvamatte vā. "
188934,64,841,38,49,1,84,9,"So taṃ nimittaṃ suggahitaṃ karoti, sūpadhāritaṃ upadhāreti, suvavatthitaṃ vavatthapeti. "
188935,64,841,50,77,1,245,25,So taṃ nimittaṃ suggahitaṃ katvā sūpadhāritaṃ upadhāretvā suvavatthitaṃ vavatthapetvā ānisaṃsadassāvī ratanasaññī hutvā cittīkāraṃ upaṭṭhapetvā sampiyāyamāno tasmiṃ ārammaṇe cittaṃ upanibandhati‘ addhā imāya paṭipadāya jarāmaraṇamhā muccissāmī’ ti. 
188936,64,841,78,91,1,62,9,So vivicceva kāmehi… pe… paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharatī’’ ti. 
188937,64,842,2,28,1,251,24,"Tattha yena atītabhavepi sāsane vā isipabbajjāya vā pabbajitvā pathavīkasiṇe catukkapañcakajjhānāni nibbattitapubbāni, evarūpassa puññavato upanissayasampannassa akatāya pathaviyā kasitaṭṭhāne vā khalamaṇḍale vā nimittaṃ uppajjati, mallakattherassa viya. "
188938,64,842,29,36,1,80,7,Tassa kirāyasmato kasitaṭṭhānaṃ olokentassa taṃṭhānappamāṇameva nimittaṃ udapādi. 
188939,64,842,37,47,1,101,10,So taṃ vaḍḍhetvā pañcakajjhānāni nibbattetvā jhānapadaṭṭhānaṃ vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
188940,64,843,2,16,1,138,13,"Yo panevaṃ akatādhikāro hoti, tena ācariyasantike uggahitakammaṭṭhānavidhānaṃ avirādhetvā cattāro kasiṇadose pariharantena kasiṇaṃ kātabbaṃ. "
188941,64,843,17,21,1,62,4,Nīlapītalohitaodātasambhedavasena hi cattāro pathavīkasiṇadosā. 
188942,64,843,22,32,1,103,10,Tasmā nīlādivaṇṇaṃ mattikaṃ aggahetvā gaṅgāvahe mattikāsadisāya aruṇavaṇṇāya mattikāya kasiṇaṃ kātabbaṃ. 
188943,64,843,33,41,1,64,7,Tañca kho vihāramajjhe sāmaṇerādīnaṃ sañcaraṇaṭṭhāne na kātabbaṃ. 
188944,64,843,42,54,1,103,12,Vihārapaccante pana paṭicchannaṭṭhāne pabbhāre vā paṇṇasālāya vā saṃhārimaṃ vā tatraṭṭhakaṃ vā kātabbaṃ. 
188945,64,843,55,75,1,184,19,Tatra saṃhārimaṃ catūsu daṇḍakesu pilotikaṃ vā cammaṃ vā kaṭasārakaṃ vā bandhitvā tattha apanītatiṇamūlasakkharakathalikāya sumadditāya mattikāya vuttappamāṇaṃ vaṭṭaṃ limpetvā kātabbaṃ. 
188946,64,843,76,81,1,49,5,Taṃ parikammakāle bhūmiyaṃ attharitvā oloketabbaṃ. 
188947,64,843,82,90,1,87,8,Tatraṭṭhakaṃ bhūmiyaṃ padumakaṇṇikākārena khāṇuke ākoṭetvā vallīhi vinandhitvā kātabbaṃ. 
188948,64,843,91,106,1,143,14,"Yadi sā mattikā nappahoti, adho aññaṃ pakkhipitvā uparibhāge suparisodhitāya aruṇavaṇṇāya mattikāya vidatthicaturaṅgulavitthāraṃ vaṭṭaṃ kātabbaṃ. "
188949,64,843,107,121,1,68,10,Etadeva hi pamāṇaṃ sandhāya‘‘ suppamattaṃ vā sarāvamattaṃ vā’’ ti vuttaṃ.
188950,64,843,122,133,1,58,7,‘‘ Sāntake no anantake’’ tiādi panassa paricchedatthāya vuttaṃ. 
188951,64,844,2,12,1,82,7,56. Tasmā evaṃ vuttappamāṇaparicchedaṃ katvā rukkhapāṇikā visabhāgavaṇṇaṃ samuṭṭhapeti. 
188952,64,844,13,34,1,220,21,Tasmā taṃ aggahetvā pāsāṇapāṇikāya ghaṃsetvā samaṃ bherītalasadisaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānaṃ sammajjitvā nhatvā āgantvā kasiṇamaṇḍalato aḍḍhateyyahatthantare padese paññatte vidatthicaturaṅgulapādake suatthate pīṭhe nisīditabbaṃ. 
188953,64,844,35,46,1,81,10,"Tato dūratare nisinnassa hi kasiṇaṃ na upaṭṭhāti, āsannatare kasiṇadosā paññāyanti. "
188954,64,844,47,57,1,77,9,"Uccatare nisinnena gīvaṃ onamitvā oloketabbaṃ hoti, nīcatare jaṇṇukāni rujanti. "
188955,64,844,58,114,1,478,44,Tasmā vuttanayeneva nisīditvā‘‘ appassādā kāmā’’ tiādinā nayena kāmesu ādīnavaṃ paccavekkhitvā kāmanissaraṇe sabbadukkhasamatikkamupāyabhūte nekkhamme jātābhilāsena buddhadhammasaṅghaguṇānussaraṇena pītipāmojjaṃ janayitvā‘‘ ayaṃ dāni sā sabbabuddha paccekabuddha ariyasāvakehi paṭipannā nekkhammapaṭipadā’’ ti paṭipattiyā sañjātagāravena‘‘ addhā imāya paṭipadāya pavivekasukharasassa bhāgī bhavissāmī’’ ti ussāhaṃ janayitvā samena ākārena cakkhūni ummīletvā nimittaṃ gaṇhantena bhāvetabbaṃ. 
188956,64,845,2,14,1,88,10,"Atiummīlayato hi cakkhu kilamati, maṇḍalañca ativibhūtaṃ hoti, tenassa nimittaṃ nuppajjati. "
188957,64,845,15,27,1,90,10,"Atimandaṃ ummīlayato maṇḍalamavibhūtaṃ hoti, cittañca līnaṃ hoti, evampi nimittaṃ nuppajjati. "
188958,64,845,28,46,1,158,16,"Tasmā ādāsatale mukhanimittadassinā viya samenākārena cakkhūni ummīletvā nimittaṃ gaṇhantena bhāvetabbaṃ, na vaṇṇo paccavekkhitabbo, na lakkhaṇaṃ manasikātabbaṃ. "
