189143,64,913,2,2,1,26,1,Nimittābhimukhapaṭipādanaṃ 
189144,64,914,2,25,1,171,19,68. Tatrāyamatthadīpanā– yathā hi acheko madhukaro asukasmiṃ rukkhe pupphaṃ pupphitanti ñatvā tikkhena vegena pakkhando taṃ atikkamitvā paṭinivattento khīṇe reṇumhi sampāpuṇāti. 
189145,64,914,26,33,1,59,7,Aparo acheko mandena javena pakkhando khīṇeyeva sampāpuṇāti. 
189146,64,914,34,48,1,128,14,Cheko pana samena javena pakkhando sukhena puppharāsiṃ sampatvā yāvadicchakaṃ reṇuṃ ādāya madhuṃ sampādetvā madhurasamanubhavati. 
189147,64,915,2,24,1,167,19,"Yathā ca sallakattaantevāsikesu udakathālagate uppalapatte satthakammaṃ sikkhantesu eko acheko vegena satthaṃ pātento uppalapattaṃ dvidhā vā chindati, udake vā paveseti. "
189148,64,915,25,32,1,68,7,Aparo acheko chijjanapavesanabhayā satthakena phusitumpi na visahati. 
189149,64,915,33,48,1,126,15,Cheko pana samena payogena tattha satthapahāraṃ dassetvā pariyodātasippo hutvā tathārūpesu ṭhānesu kammaṃ katvā lābhaṃ labhati. 
189150,64,916,2,21,1,166,18,"Yathā ca yo catubyāmappamāṇaṃ makkaṭasuttamāharati, so cattāri sahassāni labhatīti raññā vutte eko achekapuriso vegena makkaṭasuttamākaḍḍhanto tahiṃ tahiṃ chindatiyeva. "
189151,64,916,22,29,1,57,7,Aparo acheko chedanabhayā hatthena phusitumpi na visahati. 
189152,64,916,30,41,1,83,11,Cheko pana koṭito paṭṭhāya samena payogena daṇḍake vedhetvā āharitvā lābhaṃ labhati. 
189153,64,917,2,12,1,80,10,Yathā ca acheko niyāmako balavavāte laṅkāraṃ pūrento nāvaṃ videsaṃ pakkhandāpeti. 
189154,64,917,13,21,1,63,8,Aparo acheko mandavāte laṅkāraṃ oropento nāvaṃ tattheva ṭhapeti. 
