189374,64,965,2,19,1,90,12,"76. Evamadhigate pana etasmiṃ tena yoginā vālavedhinā viya, sūdena viya ca ākārā pariggahetabbā. "
189375,64,965,20,43,1,171,22,"Yathā hi sukusalo dhanuggaho vālavedhāya kammaṃ kurumāno yasmiṃ vāre vālaṃ vijjhati, tasmiṃ vāre akkantapadānañca dhanudaṇḍassa ca jiyāya ca sarassa ca ākāraṃ pariggaṇheyya."
189376,64,965,44,61,1,77,13,‘‘ Evaṃ me ṭhitena evaṃ dhanudaṇḍaṃ evaṃ jiyaṃ evaṃ saraṃ gahetvā vālo viddho’’ ti. 
189377,64,965,62,72,1,72,10,So tato paṭṭhāya tatheva te ākāre sampādento avirādhetvā vālaṃ vijjheyya. 
189378,64,965,73,101,1,193,24,Evameva yogināpi‘‘ imaṃ nāma me bhojanaṃ bhuñjitvā evarūpaṃ puggalaṃ sevamānena evarūpe senāsane iminā nāma iriyāpathena imasmiṃ kāle idaṃ adhigatan’’ ti ete bhojanasappāyādayo ākārā pariggahetabbā. 
189379,64,965,102,121,1,121,17,"Evañhi so naṭṭhe vā tasmiṃ te ākāre sampādetvā puna uppādetuṃ, appaguṇaṃ vā paguṇaṃ karonto punappunaṃ appetuṃ sakkhissati. "
189380,64,966,2,38,1,260,34,"Yathā ca kusalo sūdo bhattāraṃ parivisanto tassa yaṃ yaṃ ruciyā bhuñjati, taṃ taṃ sallakkhetvā tato paṭṭhāya tādisameva upanāmento lābhassa bhāgī hoti, evamayampi adhigatakkhaṇe bhojanādayo ākāre gahetvā te sampādento naṭṭhe naṭṭhe punappunaṃ appanāya lābhī hoti. "
189381,64,966,39,48,1,63,9,Tasmā tena vālavedhinā viya sūdena viya ca ākārā pariggahetabbā. 
189382,64,966,49,52,1,24,3,Vuttampi cetaṃ bhagavatā–
189383,64,967,2,28,1,220,23,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo sūdo rājānaṃ vā rājamahāmattaṃ vā nānaccayehi sūpehi paccupaṭṭhito assa ambilaggehipi tittakaggehipi kaṭukaggehipi madhuraggehipi khārikehipi akhārikehipi loṇikehipi aloṇikehipi. "
189384,64,967,29,96,1,359,54,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo sūdo sakassa bhattu nimittaṃ uggaṇhāti‘ idaṃ vā me ajja bhattu sūpeyyaṃ ruccati, imassa vā abhiharati, imassa vā bahuṃ gaṇhāti, imassa vā vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, ambilaggaṃ vā me ajja bhattu sūpeyyaṃ ruccati, ambilaggassa vā abhiharati, ambilaggassa vā bahuṃ gaṇhāti, ambilaggassa vā vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati… pe… aloṇikassa vā vaṇṇaṃ bhāsatī’ ti. "
189385,64,967,97,117,1,109,16,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo sūdo lābhī ceva hoti acchādanassa, lābhī vetanassa, lābhī abhihārānaṃ. "
189386,64,967,118,121,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
189387,64,967,122,137,1,82,12,"Tathā hi so, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo sūdo sakassa bhattu nimittaṃ uggaṇhāti. "
189388,64,967,138,169,1,205,25,"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco paṇḍito byatto kusalo bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati… pe… vedanāsu vedanā… citte cittā… dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
189389,64,967,170,184,1,105,12,"Tassa dhammesu dhammānupassino viharato cittaṃ samādhiyati, upakkilesā pahīyanti, so taṃ nimittaṃ uggaṇhāti. "
189390,64,967,185,202,1,116,14,"Sa kho so, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo bhikkhu lābhī ceva hoti diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārānaṃ, lābhī satisampajaññassa. "
189391,64,967,203,206,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
189392,64,967,207,234,1,90,13,"Tathā hi so, bhikkhave, paṇḍito byatto kusalo bhikkhu sakassa cittassa nimittaṃ uggaṇhātī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.374). "
189393,64,968,2,13,1,87,10,"Nimittaggahaṇena cassa puna te ākāre sampādayato appanāmattameva ijjhati, na ciraṭṭhānaṃ. "
189394,64,968,14,20,1,67,6,Ciraṭṭhānaṃ pana samādhiparibandhānaṃ dhammānaṃ suvisodhitattā hoti. 
189395,64,968,21,69,1,457,43,"Yo hi bhikkhu kāmādīnavapaccavekkhaṇādīhi kāmacchandaṃ na suṭṭhu vikkhambhetvā, kāyapassaddhivasena kāyaduṭṭhullaṃ na suppaṭipassaddhaṃ katvā, ārambhadhātumanasikārādivasena thinamiddhaṃ na suṭṭhu paṭivinodetvā, samathanimittamanasikārādivasena uddhaccakukkuccaṃ na susamūhataṃ katvā, aññepi samādhiparibandhe dhamme na suṭṭhu visodhetvā jhānaṃ samāpajjati, so avisodhitaṃ āsayaṃ paviṭṭhabhamaro viya avisuddhaṃ uyyānaṃ paviṭṭharājā viya ca khippameva nikkhamati. "
189396,64,968,70,93,1,205,22,"Yo pana samādhiparibandhe dhamme suṭṭhu visodhetvā jhānaṃ samāpajjati, so suvisodhitaṃ āsayaṃ paviṭṭhabhamaro viya suparisuddhaṃ uyyānaṃ paviṭṭharājā viya ca sakalampi divasabhāgaṃ antosamāpattiyaṃyeva hoti. "
189397,64,968,94,96,1,13,2,Tenāhu porāṇā–
189398,64,969,2,8,1,32,5,"‘ ‘ Kāmesu chandaṃ paṭighaṃ vinodaye, "
189399,64,970,2,4,1,34,2,Uddhaccamiddhaṃ vicikicchapañcamaṃ; 
189400,64,971,2,4,1,26,2,"Vivekapāmojjakarena cetasā, "
189401,64,972,2,9,1,34,5,Rājāva suddhantagato tahiṃ rame’’ ti. 
189402,64,973,2,8,1,75,6,Tasmā ciraṭṭhitikāmena paribandhakadhamme visodhetvā jhānaṃ samāpajjitabbaṃ. 
189403,64,973,9,13,1,70,4,Cittabhāvanāvepullatthañca yathāladdhaṃ paṭibhāganimittaṃ vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. 
189404,64,973,14,22,1,48,7,Tassa dve vaḍḍhanābhūmiyo upacāraṃ vā appanaṃ vā. 
189405,64,973,23,31,1,57,8,Upacāraṃ patvāpi hi taṃ vaḍḍhetuṃ vaṭṭati appanaṃ patvāpi. 
189406,64,973,32,37,1,39,5,Ekasmiṃ pana ṭhāne avassaṃ vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. 
189407,64,973,38,48,1,58,6,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ yathāladdhaṃ paṭibhāganimittaṃ vaḍḍhetabban’’ ti. 
189408,64,974,2,2,1,19,1,Nimittavaḍḍhananayo 
189409,64,975,2,46,1,449,37,"77. Tatrāyaṃ vaḍḍhananayo, tena yoginā taṃ nimittaṃ pattavaḍḍhanapūvavaḍḍhanabhattavaḍḍhanalatāvaḍḍhanadussavaḍḍhanayogena avaḍḍhetvā yathā nāma kassako kasitabbaṭṭhānaṃ naṅgalena paricchinditvā paricchedabbhantare kasati, yathā vā pana bhikkhū sīmaṃ bandhantā paṭhamaṃ nimittāni sallakkhetvā pacchā bandhanti, evameva tassa yathāladdhassa nimittassa anukkamena ekaṅguladvaṅgulativaṅgulacaturaṅgulamattaṃ manasā paricchinditvā yathāparicchedaṃ vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. "
189410,64,975,47,51,1,36,4,Aparicchinditvā pana na vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. 
189411,64,975,52,64,1,188,12,Tato vidatthiratanapamukhapariveṇavihārasīmānaṃ gāmanigamajanapadarajjasamuddasīmānañca paricchedavasena vaḍḍhayantena cakkavāḷaparicchedena vā tato vāpi uttari paricchinditvā vaḍḍhetabbaṃ. 
189412,64,976,2,30,1,259,27,"Yathā hi haṃsapotakā pakkhānaṃ uṭṭhitakālato paṭṭhāya parittaṃ parittaṃ padesaṃ uppatantā paricayaṃ katvā anukkamena candimasūriyasantikaṃ gacchanti, evameva bhikkhu vuttanayena nimittaṃ paricchinditvā vaḍḍhento yāva cakkavāḷaparicchedā tato vā uttari vaḍḍheti. "
189413,64,976,31,41,1,138,10,Athassa taṃ nimittaṃ vaḍḍhitavaḍḍhitaṭṭhāne pathaviyā ukkūlavikūlanadīviduggapabbatavisamesu saṅkusatasamabbhāhataṃ usabhacammaṃ viya hoti. 
189414,64,977,2,12,1,110,9,"Tasmiṃ pana nimitte pattapaṭhamajjhānena ādikammikena samāpajjanabahulena bhavitabbaṃ, na paccavekkhaṇabahulena. "
189415,64,977,13,20,1,73,7,Paccavekkhaṇabahulassa hi jhānaṅgāni thūlāni dubbalāni hutvā upaṭṭhahanti. 
189416,64,977,21,29,1,69,8,Athassa tāni evaṃ upaṭṭhitattā upari ussukkanāya paccayataṃ āpajjanti. 
189417,64,977,30,43,1,94,12,"So appaguṇe jhāne ussukkamāno pattapaṭhamajjhānā ca parihāyati, na ca sakkoti dutiyaṃ pāpuṇituṃ. "
189418,64,977,44,46,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
189419,64,978,2,17,1,91,12,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gāvī pabbateyyā bālā abyattā akhettaññū akusalā visame pabbate carituṃ. "
189420,64,978,18,37,1,131,15,"Tassā evamassa‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ agatapubbañceva disaṃ gaccheyyaṃ, akhāditapubbāni ca tiṇāni khādeyyaṃ, apītapubbāni ca pānīyāni piveyyan’ ti. "
189421,64,978,38,67,1,187,25,"Sā purimaṃ pādaṃ na supatiṭṭhitaṃ patiṭṭhāpetvā pacchimaṃ pādaṃ uddhareyya, sā na ceva agatapubbaṃ disaṃ gaccheyya, na ca akhāditapubbāni tiṇāni khādeyya, na ca apītapubbāni pānīyāni piveyya. "
189422,64,978,68,81,1,77,9,Yasmiñcassā padese ṭhitāya evamassa‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ agatapubbañceva… pe… piveyyan’ ti. 
189423,64,978,82,87,1,40,5,Tañca padesaṃ na sotthinā paccāgaccheyya. 
189424,64,978,88,92,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu ? 
189425,64,978,93,129,1,222,29,"Tathā hi sā, bhikkhave, gāvī pabbateyyā bālā abyattā akhettaññū akusalā visame pabbate carituṃ, evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu bālo abyatto akhettaññū akusalo vivicceva kāmehi… pe… paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ. "
189426,64,978,130,161,1,176,23,"So taṃ nimittaṃ nāsevati, na bhāveti, na bahulīkaroti, na svādhiṭṭhitaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, tassa evaṃ hoti‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā… pe… dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ ti. "
189427,64,978,162,174,1,79,10,So na sakkoti vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā… pe… dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ. 
189428,64,978,175,190,1,86,11,Tassevaṃ hoti‘ yaṃnūnāhaṃ vivicceva kāmehi… pe… paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ ti. 
189429,64,978,191,203,1,71,10,So na sakkoti vivicceva kāmehi… pe… paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharituṃ. 
189430,64,978,204,238,1,149,20,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ubhato bhaṭṭho ubhato parihīno, seyyathāpi sā gāvī pabbateyyā bālā abyattā akhettaññū akusalā visame pabbate caritun’’ ti( a. ni.9.35). "
189431,64,979,2,9,1,77,7,Tasmānena tasmiṃyeva tāva paṭhamajjhāne pañcahākārehi ciṇṇavasinā bhavitabbaṃ. 
189432,64,980,2,2,1,14,1,Pañcavasīkathā 
189433,64,981,2,17,1,97,8,"78. Tatrimā pañca vasiyo āvajjanavasī, samāpajjanavasī, adhiṭṭhānavasī, vuṭṭhānavasī, paccavekkhaṇavasīti. "
189434,64,981,18,29,1,112,10,"Paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ yatthicchakaṃ yadicchakaṃ yāvadicchakaṃ āvajjeti, āvajjanāya dandhāyitattaṃ natthīti āvajjanavasī. "
189435,64,981,30,42,1,98,9,"Paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ yatthicchakaṃ… pe… samāpajjati, samāpajjanāya dandhāyitattaṃ natthīti samāpajjanavasī. "
189436,64,981,43,46,1,25,3,Evaṃ sesāpi vitthāretabbā. 
189437,64,982,2,20,1,182,17,"Ayaṃ panettha atthappakāsanā, paṭhamajjhānato vuṭṭhāya paṭhamaṃ vitakkaṃ āvajjayato bhavaṅgaṃ upacchinditvā uppannāvajjanānantaraṃ vitakkārammaṇāneva cattāri pañca vā javanāni javanti. "
189438,64,982,21,46,1,175,21,"Tato dve bhavaṅgāni, tato puna vicārārammaṇaṃ āvajjanaṃ, vuttanayāneva javanānīti evaṃ pañcasu jhānaṅgesu yadā nirantaraṃ cittaṃ pesetuṃ sakkoti, athassa āvajjanavasī siddhā hoti. "
189439,64,982,47,60,1,89,11,"Ayaṃ pana matthakappattā vasī bhagavato yamakapāṭihāriye labbhati , aññesaṃ vā evarūpe kāle. "
189440,64,982,61,67,1,44,6,Ito paraṃ sīghatarā āvajjanavasī nāma natthi. 
189441,64,983,2,11,1,113,9,Āyasmato pana mahāmoggallānassa nandopanandanāgarājadamane viya sīghaṃ samāpajjanasamatthatā samāpajjanavasī nāma. 
189442,64,984,2,11,1,83,9,Accharāmattaṃ vā dasaccharāmattaṃ vā khaṇaṃ ṭhapetuṃ samatthatā adhiṭṭhānavasī nāma. 
189443,64,984,12,18,1,52,6,Tatheva lahuṃ vuṭṭhātuṃ samatthatā vuṭṭhānavasī nāma. 
189444,64,984,19,24,1,70,5,Tadubhayadassanatthaṃ buddharakkhitattherassa vatthuṃ kathetuṃ vaṭṭati. 
189445,64,985,2,32,1,336,30,So hāyasmā upasampadāya aṭṭhavassiko hutvā therambatthale mahārohaṇaguttattherassa gilānupaṭṭhānaṃ āgatānaṃ tiṃsamattānaṃ iddhimantasahassānaṃ majjhe nisinno therassa yāguṃ paṭiggāhayamānaṃ upaṭṭhākanāgarājānaṃ gahessāmīti ākāsato pakkhandantaṃ supaṇṇarājānaṃ disvā tāvadeva pabbataṃ nimminitvā nāgarājānaṃ bāhāyaṃ gahetvā tattha pāvisi. 
189446,64,985,33,38,1,40,5,Supaṇṇarājā pabbate pahāraṃ datvā palāyi. 
189447,64,985,39,41,1,13,2,Mahāthero āha–
189448,64,985,42,57,1,62,8,"‘‘ sace, āvuso, buddharakkhito nābhavissa, sabbeva gārayhā assāmā’’ ti. "
189449,64,986,2,7,1,47,5,Paccavekkhaṇavasī pana āvajjanavasiyā eva vuttā. 
189450,64,986,8,12,1,53,4,Paccavekkhaṇajavanāneva hi tattha āvajjanānantarānīti. 
189451,64,987,2,2,1,17,1,Dutiyajjhānakathā 
189452,64,988,2,37,1,271,27,"79. Imāsu pana pañcasu vasīsu ciṇṇavasinā paguṇapaṭhamajjhānato vuṭṭhāya‘‘ ayaṃ samāpatti āsannanīvaraṇapaccatthikā, vitakkavicārānaṃ oḷārikattā aṅgadubbalā’’ ti ca tattha dosaṃ disvā dutiyajjhānaṃ santato manasikatvā paṭhamajjhāne nikantiṃ pariyādāya dutiyādhigamāya yogo kātabbo. "
189453,64,988,38,90,1,405,40,"Athassa yadā paṭhamajjhānā vuṭṭhāya satassa sampajānassa jhānaṅgāni paccavekkhato vitakkavicārā oḷārikato upaṭṭhahanti, pītisukhañceva cittekaggatā ca santato upaṭṭhāti, tadāssa oḷārikaṅgaṃ pahānāya santaaṅgapaṭilābhāya ca tadeva nimittaṃ‘‘ pathavī pathavī’’ ti punappunaṃ manasikaroto‘‘ idāni dutiyajjhānaṃ uppajjissatī’’ ti bhavaṅgaṃ upacchinditvā tadeva pathavīkasiṇaṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā manodvārāvajjanaṃ uppajjati . "
189454,64,988,91,103,1,102,11,"Tato tasmiṃyevārammaṇe cattāri pañca vā javanāni javanti, yesamavasāne ekaṃ rūpāvacaraṃ dutiyajjhānikaṃ. "
189455,64,988,104,107,1,38,3,Sesāni vuttappakārāneva kāmāvacarānīti. 
189456,64,989,2,18,1,158,16,Ettāvatā cesa vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
189457,64,989,19,29,1,129,10,Evamanena dvaṅgavippahīnaṃ tivaṅgasamannāgataṃ tividhakalyāṇaṃ dasalakkhaṇasampannaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ adhigataṃ hoti pathavīkasiṇaṃ. 
189458,64,990,2,22,1,143,15,"80. Tattha vitakkavicārānaṃ {vūpasamā}ti vitakkassa ca vicārassa cāti imesaṃ dvinnaṃ vūpasamā samatikkamā, dutiyajjhānakkhaṇe apātubhāvāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
189459,64,990,23,30,1,64,7,Tattha kiñcāpi dutiyajjhāne sabbepi paṭhamajjhānadhammā na santi. 
189460,64,990,31,38,1,46,6,"Aññeyeva hi paṭhamajjhāne phassādayo, aññe idha. "
189461,64,990,39,60,1,170,17,Oḷārikassa pana oḷārikassa aṅgassa samatikkamā paṭhamajjhānato paresaṃ dutiyajjhānādīnaṃ adhigamo hotīti dīpanatthaṃ‘‘ vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā’’ ti evaṃ vuttanti veditabbaṃ. 
189462,64,991,2,6,1,42,4,Ajjhattan ti idha niyakajjhattamadhippetaṃ. 
189463,64,991,7,18,1,54,7,Vibhaṅge pana‘‘ ajjhattaṃ paccattan’’ ti ettakameva vuttaṃ. 
189464,64,991,19,31,1,95,11,"Yasmā ca niyakajjhattamadhippetaṃ, tasmā attani jātaṃ attano santāne nibbattanti ayamettha attho. "
189465,64,991,32,37,1,43,5,Sampasādanan ti sampasādanaṃ vuccati saddhā. 
189466,64,991,38,41,1,39,3,Sampasādanayogato jhānampi sampasādanaṃ. 
189467,64,991,42,45,1,32,3,Nīlavaṇṇayogato nīlavatthaṃ viya. 
189468,64,991,46,59,1,132,12,"Yasmā vā taṃ jhānaṃ sampasādanasamannāgatattā vitakkavicārakkhobhavūpasamanena ca cetaso sampasādayati, tasmāpi sampasādananti vuttaṃ. "
189469,64,991,60,67,1,73,7,Imasmiñca atthavikappe sampasādanaṃ cetasoti evaṃ padasambandho veditabbo. 
189470,64,991,68,76,1,74,8,Purimasmiṃ pana atthavikappe cetasoti etaṃ ekodibhāvena saddhiṃ yojetabbaṃ. 
189471,64,992,2,15,1,101,11,"Tatrāyamatthayojanā , eko udetīti ekodi, vitakkavicārehi anajjhārūḷhattā aggo seṭṭho hutvā udetīti attho. "
189472,64,992,16,21,1,30,5,Seṭṭhopi hi loke ekoti vuccati. 
189473,64,992,22,30,1,63,8,Vitakkavicāravirahato vā eko asahāyo hutvā itipi vattuṃ vaṭṭati. 
189474,64,992,31,40,1,56,7,"Atha vā sampayuttadhamme udāyatīti udi, uṭṭhāpetīti attho. "
189475,64,992,41,52,1,63,9,"Seṭṭhaṭṭhena eko ca so udi cāti ekodi, samādhissetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
189476,64,992,53,61,1,65,8,Iti imaṃ ekodiṃ bhāveti vaḍḍhetīti idaṃ dutiyajjhānaṃ ekodibhāvaṃ. 
189477,64,992,62,79,1,91,14,"So panāyaṃ ekodi yasmā cetaso, na sattassa, na jīvassa, tasmā etaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvanti vuttaṃ. "
189478,64,993,2,24,1,131,16,"Nanu cāyaṃ saddhā paṭhamajjhānepi atthi, ayañca ekodināmako samādhi, atha kasmā idameva‘‘ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvañcā’’ ti vuttanti. "
189479,64,993,25,47,1,152,16,"Vuccate, aduñhi paṭhamajjhānaṃ vitakkavicārakkhobhena vīcitaraṅgasamākulamiva jalaṃ na suppasannaṃ hoti, tasmā satiyāpi saddhāya‘‘ sampasādanan’’ ti na vuttaṃ. "
189480,64,993,48,65,1,88,12,"Na suppasannattāyeva cettha samādhipi na suṭṭhu pākaṭo, tasmā‘‘ ekodibhāvan’’ tipi na vuttaṃ. "
189481,64,993,66,84,1,166,16,"Imasmiṃ pana jhāne vitakkavicārapalibodhābhāvena laddhokāsā balavatī saddhā, balavasaddhāsahāyapaṭilābheneva ca samādhipi pākaṭo, tasmā idameva evaṃ vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
189482,64,993,85,95,1,69,8,Vibhaṅge pana‘‘ sampasādananti yā saddhā saddahanā okappanā abhippasādo. 
189483,64,993,96,110,1,75,10,Cetaso ekodibhāvanti yā cittassa ṭhiti… pe… sammāsamādhī’’ ti ettakameva vuttaṃ. 
189484,64,993,111,129,1,119,16,"Evaṃ vuttena pana tena saddhiṃ ayamatthavaṇṇanā yathā na virujjhati, aññadatthu saṃsandati ceva sameti ca, evaṃ veditabbā. "
189485,64,994,2,17,1,86,11,"81. Avitakkaṃ avicāran ti bhāvanāya pahīnattā etasmiṃ, etassa vā vitakko natthīti avitakkaṃ. "
189486,64,994,18,21,1,23,3,Imināva nayena avicāraṃ. 
189487,64,994,22,55,1,183,23,"Vibhaṅgepi vuttaṃ‘‘ iti ayañca vitakko ayañca vicāro santā honti samitā vūpasantā atthaṅgatā abbhatthaṅgatā appitā byappitā sositā visositā byantikatā, tena vuccati avitakkaṃ avicāran’’ ti( vibha.576). "
189488,64,995,2,27,1,114,16,"Etthāha ‘‘ nanu ca‘ vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā’ ti imināpi ayamattho siddho, atha kasmā puna vuttaṃ‘ avitakkaṃ avicāran’ ti’’. "
189489,64,995,28,36,1,60,6,"Vuccate, evametaṃ siddhovāyamattho, na panetaṃ tadatthadīpakaṃ. "
189490,64,995,37,59,1,177,18,Nanu avocumha‘‘ oḷārikassa pana oḷārikassa aṅgassa samatikkamā paṭhamajjhānato paresaṃ dutiyajjhānādīnaṃ samadhigamo hotīti dassanatthaṃ vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamāti evaṃ vuttan’’ ti. 
189491,64,996,2,10,1,71,7,"Apica vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā idaṃ sampasādanaṃ, na kilesakālussiyassa. "
189492,64,996,11,29,1,174,14,"Vitakkavicārānañca vūpasamā ekodibhāvaṃ, na upacārajjhānamiva nīvaraṇappahānā , paṭhamajjhānamiva ca na aṅgapātubhāvāti evaṃ sampasādanaekodibhāvānaṃ hetuparidīpakamidaṃ vacanaṃ. "
189493,64,996,30,50,1,206,18,"Tathā vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā idaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ, na tatiyacatutthajjhānāni viya cakkhuviññāṇādīni viya ca abhāvāti evaṃ avitakkaavicārabhāvassa hetuparidīpakañca, na vitakkavicārābhāvamattaparidīpakaṃ. "
189494,64,996,51,62,1,77,7,Vitakkavicārābhāvamattaparidīpakameva pana‘‘ avitakkaṃ avicāran’’ ti idaṃ vacanaṃ. 
189495,64,996,63,67,1,36,4,Tasmā purimaṃ vatvāpi vattabbamevāti. 
189496,64,997,2,9,1,73,7,Samādhijan ti paṭhamajjhānasamādhito sampayuttasamādhito vā jātanti attho. 
189497,64,997,10,46,1,230,25,"Tattha kiñcāpi paṭhamampi sampayuttasamādhito jātaṃ, atha kho ayameva samādhi‘‘ samādhī’’ ti vattabbataṃ arahati vitakkavicārakkhobhavirahena ativiya acalattā, suppasannattā ca, tasmā imassa vaṇṇabhaṇanatthaṃ idameva‘‘ samādhijan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
189498,64,997,47,50,1,31,3,Pītisukhanti idaṃ vuttanayameva. 
189499,64,998,2,6,1,34,4,Dutiyan ti gaṇanānupubbatā dutiyaṃ. 
189500,64,998,7,11,1,36,4,Idaṃ dutiyaṃ samāpajjatītipi dutiyaṃ. 
189501,64,998,12,28,1,120,11,"Yaṃ pana vuttaṃ‘‘ dvaṅgavippahīnaṃ tivaṅgasamannāgatan’’ ti, tattha vitakkavicārānaṃ pahānavasena dvaṅgavippahīnatā veditabbā. "
189502,64,998,29,40,1,90,10,"Yathā ca paṭhamajjhānassa upacārakkhaṇe nīvaraṇāni pahīyanti, na tathā imassa vitakkavicārā. "
