189505,64,998,58,67,1,90,9,Pīti sukhaṃ cittekaggatāti imesaṃ pana tiṇṇaṃ uppattivasena tivaṅgasamannāgatatā veditabbā. 
189506,64,998,68,95,1,129,17,"Tasmā yaṃ vibhaṅge‘‘ jhānanti sampasādo pīti sukhaṃ cittassa ekaggatā’’ ti( vibha.580) vuttaṃ, taṃ saparikkhāraṃ jhānaṃ dassetuṃ pariyāyena vuttaṃ. "
