189509,64,998,109,136,1,77,11,"‘‘ katamaṃ tasmiṃ samaye tivaṅgikaṃ jhānaṃ hoti, pīti sukhaṃ cittassa ekaggatā’’ ti( dha. sa.161; vibha.628). "
189510,64,998,137,140,1,33,3,Sesaṃ paṭhamajjhāne vuttanayameva. 
189511,64,999,2,2,1,17,1,Tatiyajjhānakathā 
189512,64,1000,2,63,1,383,39,"82. Evamadhigate pana tasmimpi vuttanayeneva pañcahākārehi ciṇṇavasinā hutvā paguṇadutiyajjhānato vuṭṭhāya‘‘ ayaṃ samāpatti āsannavitakkavicārapaccatthikā,‘ yadeva tattha pītigataṃ cetaso uppilāvitaṃ, etenetaṃ oḷārikaṃ akkhāyatī’ ti( dī. ni.1.96) vuttāya pītiyā oḷārikattā aṅgadubbalā’’ ti ca tattha dosaṃ disvā tatiyajjhānaṃ santato manasikaritvā dutiyajjhāne nikantiṃ pariyādāya tatiyādhigamāya yogo kātabbo. "
189513,64,1000,64,81,1,148,16,"Athassa yadā dutiyajjhānato vuṭṭhāya satassa sampajānassa jhānaṅgāni paccavekkhato pīti oḷārikato upaṭṭhāti, sukhañceva ekaggatā ca santato upaṭṭhāti. "
189514,64,1000,82,113,1,236,23,Tadāssa oḷārikaṅgappahānāya santaaṅgapaṭilābhāya ca tadeva nimittaṃ‘‘ pathavī pathavī’’ ti punappunaṃ manasikaroto‘‘ idāni tatiyajjhānaṃ uppajjissatī’’ ti bhavaṅgaṃ upacchinditvā tadeva pathavīkasiṇaṃ ārammaṇaṃ katvā manodvārāvajjanaṃ uppajjati. 
189515,64,1000,114,131,1,139,15,"Tato tasmiṃyevārammaṇe cattāri pañca vā javanāni javanti, yesaṃ avasāne ekaṃ rūpāvacaraṃ tatiyajjhānikaṃ, sesāni vuttanayeneva kāmāvacarānīti. "
189516,64,1000,132,176,1,199,26,"Ettāvatā ca panesa pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati sato ca sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti upekkhako satimā sukhavihārīti, tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharatīti( dī. ni.1.230; dha. sa.163). "
189517,64,1000,177,187,1,129,10,Evamanena ekaṅgavippahīnaṃ duvaṅgasamannāgataṃ tividhakalyāṇaṃ dasalakkhaṇasampannaṃ tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ adhigataṃ hoti pathavīkasiṇaṃ. 
189518,64,1001,2,18,1,89,12,83. Tattha pītiyā ca {virāgā}ti virāgo nāma vuttappakārāya pītiyā jigucchanaṃ vā samatikkamo vā. 
189519,64,1001,19,32,1,100,12,"Ubhinnaṃ pana antarā casaddo sampiṇḍanattho, so vūpasamaṃ vā sampiṇḍeti vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamaṃ vā. "
189520,64,1001,33,54,1,107,16,"Tattha yadā vūpasamameva sampiṇḍeti, tadā‘‘ pītiyā ca virāgā kiñca bhiyyo vūpasamā cā’’ ti evaṃ yojanā veditabbā. "
189521,64,1001,55,75,1,107,15,"Imissā ca yojanāya virāgo jigucchanattho hoti, tasmā‘‘ pītiyā jigucchanā ca vūpasamā cā’’ ti ayamattho daṭṭhabbo. "
189522,64,1001,76,98,1,131,16,"Yadā pana vitakkavicāravūpasamaṃ sampiṇḍeti, tadā‘‘ pītiyā ca virāgā, kiñca bhiyyo vitakkavicārānañca vūpasamā’’ ti evaṃ yojanā veditabbā. "
189523,64,1001,99,119,1,127,15,"Imissā ca yojanāya virāgo samatikkamanattho hoti, tasmā‘‘ pītiyā ca samatikkamā vitakkavicārānañca vūpasamā’’ ti ayamattho daṭṭhabbo. "
189524,64,1002,2,13,1,122,10,"Kāmañcete vitakkavicārā dutiyajjhāneyeva vūpasantā, imassa pana jhānassa maggaparidīpanatthaṃ vaṇṇabhaṇanatthañcetaṃ vuttaṃ. "
189525,64,1002,14,27,1,104,11,"Vitakkavicārānañca vūpasamāti hi vutte idaṃ paññāyati, nūna vitakkavicāravūpasamo maggo imassa jhānassāti. "
189526,64,1002,28,95,1,273,27,"Yathā ca tatiye ariyamagge appahīnānampi sakkāyadiṭṭhādīnaṃ‘‘ pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ pahānā’’ ti( dī. ni.1.373; ma. ni.2.133; saṃ. ni.5.184; a. ni.3.88) evaṃ pahānaṃ vuccamānaṃ vaṇṇabhaṇanaṃ hoti, tadadhigamāya ussukkānaṃ ussāhajanakaṃ, evameva idha avūpasantānampi vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamo vuccamāno vaṇṇabhaṇanaṃ hoti. "
