189528,64,1003,2,13,1,58,7,84. Upekkhako ca {viharatī}ti ettha upapattito ikkhatīti upekkhā. 
189529,64,1003,14,21,1,49,6,"Samaṃ passati, apakkhapatitā hutvā passatīti attho. "
